        "The plan does not mention checking network connectivity before attempting the download"
      ],
      "suggested_improvements": [
        "Specify the exact official Red Hat URL for downloading the GPG key (e.g., https://www.redhat.com/security/data/primary.txt)",
        "Include fingerprint verification of the downloaded key against known good fingerprints before importing",
        "Add a step to check for network connectivity before attempting to download the key",
